  mobile revenues per user, with mobile ARPU measured on 
  a per line basis. 
 Postpaid Customers: Consumer customers with mobile lines 
  activated 
 Postpaid Lines: Postpaid mobile lines activated 
 Mobile Penetration: Fixed and mobile customers over fixed 
  customers and is measured at the end of the period 
 Quad Play: Customers with four services (pay-TV, fixed 
  voice, broadband and mobile) over total customer base 
  and is measured at the end of the period 
  AOP: Average number over the relevant period 
 
